data.description: SUMMER IS HERE! Your Lake house awaits! Where you say? Rustling Oaks and the home is just 100ft  from Richland Chambers lake. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits on 1 acre. Features include open concept kitchen with breakfast bar, a huge master suite with walk in closet. The garage was split making , office space or bonus room. Just leaving parking for your golf cart, lawn mower or motorcycle. From the front porch have a lake view. The large oak trees add a the perfect setting to sit and hear the leaves, rustle and the birds sing. The roof, landscaping, and water heaters were replaced in this last year! There is also a private boat ramp for residents to use!
